citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 925 am on
10-OCT-18.
Inspector arrived at 925 am, knocked at front door with no answer, called phone number on file and left message,
waited 30 minutes before leaving facility.
